owl:Ontology.terms:description: The ReproduceMe-Microscopy ontology, an extension of the ReproduceMe-Core ontology, is a part of the ReproduceMe Ontology Network. It consists of concepts and relations from biological imaging and microscopy.
owl:Ontology.terms:title: The ReproduceMe-Microscopy ontology
owl:Ontology.rdfs:label: The ReproduceMe-Microscopy ontology
